{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"id794833ce-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s720f"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"720f"},"text":"§ 720f.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" State jurisdiction over in-State delivery of natural gas","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id794833cf-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s720f/a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"a"},"text":"(a)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Local distribution","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"Any facility receiving natural gas from an Alaska natural gas transportation project for delivery to consumers within the State—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id794833d0-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s720f/a/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" shall be deemed to be a local distribution facility within the meaning of section 1(b) of the Natural Gas Act (","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t15/s717/b"},"text":"15 U.S.C. 717(b)","children":[],"tail":"); and"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id794833d1-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s720f/a/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" shall not be subject to the jurisdiction of the Commission.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id794833d2-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s720f/b"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"b"},"text":"(b)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Additional pipelines","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Except as provided in ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t15/s720a/d"},"text":"section 720a(d) of this title","children":[],"tail":", nothing in this chapter shall preclude or otherwise affect a future natural gas pipeline that may be constructed to deliver natural gas to Fairbanks, Anchorage, Matanuska-Susitna Valley, or the Kenai peninsula or Valdez or any other site in the State for consumption within or distribution outside the State."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id794833d3-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s720f/c"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"c"},"text":"(c)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Rate coordination","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id794833d4-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s720f/c/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" In general","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"In accordance with the Natural Gas Act [","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t15/s717"},"text":"15 U.S.C. 717","children":[],"tail":" et seq.], the Commission shall establish rates for the transportation of natural gas on any Alaska natural gas transportation project."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id794833d5-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s720f/c/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Consultation","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"In carrying out paragraph (1), the Commission, in accordance with section 17(b) of the Natural Gas Act (","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t15/s717p/b"},"text":"15 U.S.C. 717p(b)","children":[],"tail":"), shall consult with the State regarding rates (including rate settlements) applicable to natural gas transported on and delivered from the Alaska natural gas transportation project for use within the State."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"id794833d6-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/108/324/dC/s108"},"text":"Pub. L. 108–324, div. C, § 108","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2004-10-13"},"text":"Oct. 13, 2004","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/118/1261"},"text":"118 Stat. 1261","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"id794833d7-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"id794833d8-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"referencesInText","id":"id794833d9-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"References in Text","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"This chapter, referred to in subsec. (b), was in the original “this division”, meaning division C of ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/108/324"},"text":"Pub. L. 108–324","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2004-10-13"},"text":"Oct. 13, 2004","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/118/1255"},"text":"118 Stat. 1255","children":[],"tail":", which is classified principally to this chapter. For complete classification of division C to the Code, see Short Title note set out under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t15/s720"},"text":"section 720 of this title","children":[],"tail":" and Tables."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The Natural Gas Act, referred to in subsec. (c)(1), is ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1938-06-21/ch556"},"text":"act June 21, 1938, ch. 556","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/52/821"},"text":"52 Stat. 821","children":[],"tail":", which is classified generally to chapter 15B (§ 717 et seq.) of this title. For complete classification of this Act to the Code, see "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t15/s717w"},"text":"section 717w of this title","children":[],"tail":" and Tables."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
